source:
TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_SEQ_00 Quest Sync
The brusque Loporrit has a mind to do something dangerous, and has clearly heard of your proclivity for recklessness...
target:
TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_SEQ_00 Quest Sync
The brusque Loporrit has a mind to do something dangerous, and has clearly heard of your proclivity for recklessness...

source: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_TODO_02<tab>Return to the brusque Loporrit, and defeat any enemies that attack.
target: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_TODO_02<tab>Return to the brusque Loporrit, and defeat any enemies that attack.

source: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_TODO_04<tab>Deliver the systems cube to the brusque Loporrit.
target: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_TODO_04<tab>Deliver the systems cube to the brusque Loporrit.

source: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_000<tab>I hear you have a penchant for excitement and adventure, is that correct?
target: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_000<tab>I hear you have a penchant for excitement and adventure, is that correct?

source: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_001<tab>Then I assume in your travels you have doubtless heard tales of the Allagans.
target: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_001<tab>Then I assume in your travels you have doubtless heard tales of the Allagans.

source: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_A1_000_001<tab>The Allagans? Don't get me started.
target: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_A1_000_001<tab>The Allagans? Don't get me started.

source: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_A1_000_002<tab>Yes, and nearly everything wrong with the world seems to be their fault.
target: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_A1_000_002<tab>Yes, and nearly everything wrong with the world seems to be their fault.

source: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_003<tab>I ask because I have plans to survey an Allagan relic not far from here. The weapons guarding it, however, make it too dangerous for me to go alone.
target: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_003<tab>I ask because I have plans to survey an Allagan relic not far from here. The weapons guarding it, however, make it too dangerous for me to go alone.

source: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_004<tab>I trust you see where this is going. So, are you interested in a little adventure?
target: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_004<tab>I trust you see where this is going. So, are you interested in a little adventure?

source: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_005<tab>Much obliged. Now, let's be off. No time to waste.
target: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_005<tab>Much obliged. Now, let's be off. No time to waste.

source: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_010<tab>The crash site is just ahead. If you find anything that may prove useful, I'd be grateful if you could retrieve it for me.
target: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_010<tab>The crash site is just ahead. If you find anything that may prove useful, I'd be grateful if you could retrieve it for me.

source: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_013<tab>Large, isn't it? I wonder what secrets it holds...
target: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_013<tab>Large, isn't it? I wonder what secrets it holds...

source: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_SYSTEM_000_020<tab>This bit of Allagan technology is certainly fascinating. A shame it's too bulky to carry back...
target: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_SYSTEM_000_020<tab>This bit of Allagan technology is certainly fascinating. A shame it's too bulky to carry back...

source: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_SYSTEM_000_021<tab>This apparatus is offline, but appears to be transportable. You place it in your ambiguously sized bag...
target: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_SYSTEM_000_021<tab>This apparatus is offline, but appears to be transportable. You place it in your ambiguously sized bag...

source: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_030<tab>Phew. A moment longer and that drone would have alerted more...
target: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_030<tab>Phew. A moment longer and that drone would have alerted more...

source: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_031<tab>Now, did you find anything of interest?
target: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_031<tab>Now, did you find anything of interest?

source: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_033<tab>No, you're right. It must wait until we get back.
target: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_033<tab>No, you're right. It must wait until we get back.

source: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_040<tab>Safe at last. Now, show me what you found.
target: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_040<tab>Safe at last. Now, show me what you found.

source: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_041<tab>This... This is an Allagan decryption unit.
target: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_041<tab>This... This is an Allagan decryption unit.

source: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_042<tab>With it, we could read Allagan tomestones about history, science, poetry... If we had any, which we do not. An adventure for another day, I suppose.
target: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_042<tab>With it, we could read Allagan tomestones about history, science, poetry... If we had any, which we do not. An adventure for another day, I suppose.

source: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_043<tab>Nevertheless, I'm deeply excited by the prospect─as I'm sure you can tell. You have my heartfelt gratitude.
target: TEXT_AKTKZE014_04253_LOPORRIT04253_000_043<tab>Nevertheless, I'm deeply excited by the prospect─as I'm sure you can tell. You have my heartfelt gratitude.
